               The Bossiaeas are very variable. I adscribe the differences of the alpine form of B. Scolopendria entirely to the situation of the plant. I asked for specimens of Eremosyne recently;

M to G. Bentham, 10 September 1863 (in this edition as 63-09-10b), and M to G. Bentham, 24 September 1863. 
